1250
02:04:40,574 --> 02:04:43,054
That's not normally what happens.

1251
02:04:43,135 --> 02:04:49,876
So what we do is we put things over the archaeological resources to protect them from people coming in, digging, etc.

1252
02:04:50,436 --> 02:04:53,557
And in this case, we get the added benefit of having some interpretation

